<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.4">
<l>kaikaḷā lārat toḻutu toḻutuṉṉai</l>
<l>vaikalu māttiraip pōtumōr vīṭiṉṟip</l>
<l>paikoḷ pāmpēṟi yuṟaipara ṉēyuṉṉai</l>
<l>meykoḷak kāṇa virumpumeṉ kaṇkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Worshipping [and] worshipping you fully with [my] hands</l>
<l>daily and for the time of a moment, apart from a liberation,</l>
<l>of Highest one who stays mounted on a hooded serpent,</l>
<l>my eyes desire to truly see you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
